snippet.title: Java: Fart Generator (Easy Java Program For Beginners)
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- Java is one of the best programming languages you can learn, even today. So in this video, I'm going to be showing you an easy java program to help you learn java!

This fart generator takes a string and integer input from a user and displays their fart name!

Get the Java code: https://github.com/alexlorenlee/JavaTutorialCode/blob/master/Programs/Farts.java

I hope this helps you practice and learn java :) This is GREAT java practice for getting your feet wet in Java!

I hope you enjoyed java tutorial!
